    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and always garaged. It drives like a dream and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You won't find another one this clean! Come take a look, you're going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
