      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is a benchmark example of an analog driver's car in concours condition. Powered by a mid-mounted 3.8L flat-six, the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders and a clean bore-scope report. The 6-speed manual transmission is paired with a factory short-throw shifter, ensuring precise engagement and a tactile connection to the drivetrain. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis dynamics are sharp, with zero bushing play or damper fatigue. The DME report confirms no over-revs in higher ranges, and the undercarriage is immaculate with no fluid seepage. A meticulously maintained specimen with documented service history, ready for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. No scratches or dents. Smoke-free interior. Full service history. Clean title.",
      "price": 48500.0,
