    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, with a deep, mirror-like gloss entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather remains supple and rich in color, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, while every button, switch, and digital display operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by master technicians at the dealership, with a comprehensive folder of records documenting every fluid flush and inspection performed well ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of salt, rust, or road wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence. Included are all original keys, the window sticker, and a bespoke indoor car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
